## Engine decision trace

This is especially powerful.

For a finding, show a machine-readable but readable trace:

* parser recognized symbol X
* model matched source Y
* call resolved to function Z
* path remained feasible after branch A
* no sanitizer matched before sink B
* finding emitted with confidence High

This is exactly the kind of thing that builds trust.

