## Visual design direction

## Look and feel

Premium, modern, technical.

Avoid:

* overdesigned gradients everywhere
* marketing page visuals
* oversized cards wasting space
* excessive rounded toy-like UI

Prefer:

* restrained palette
* excellent typography
* subtle shadows and borders
* strong spacing rhythm
* calm dark mode and strong light mode
* dense but readable data tables

## Suggested design language

* clean monospace for code and paths
* crisp sans-serif for UI
* severity colors but used sparingly
* confidence visual treatment should be distinct from severity
* interactive graph views with clean edge rendering

## Density modes

Support:

* comfortable
* compact

Advanced users will want compact mode.

